<p><a name="Architecture" id="Architecture"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Socialist_realism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Architecture">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Architecture</span></h3>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Stalinist_architecture" title="Stalinist architecture">Stalinist architecture</a></div>
<table class="gallery" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 13px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Zaryadye.jpg" class="image" title="Zaryadye.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/Zaryadye.jpg/74px-Zaryadye.jpg" width="74" height="120" border="0" /></a></div>
