<p>Unrealized project of <a href="/wiki/Eighth_Sister_(Moscow)" title="Eighth Sister (Moscow)">Zaryadye skyscraper (Eight Sister)</a> in <a href="/wiki/Moscow" title="Moscow">Moscow</a></p>
</div>
