<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.cultinfo.ru/fulltext/1/001/008/104/892.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.cultinfo.ru/fulltext/1/001/008/104/892.htm" rel="nofollow">D.F. Markov and L.I. Timofeev, "Socialist Realism"</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Library_of_Congress_Country_Studies" title="Library of Congress Country Studies">Library of Congress Country Studies</a> - <a href="http://lcweb2.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/r?frd/cstdy:@field(DOCID+yu0035)" class="external text" title="http://lcweb2.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/r?frd/cstdy:@field(DOCID+yu0035)" rel="nofollow">Yugoslavia: <i>Introduction of Socialist Self-Management</i></a></li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.cultinfo.ru/fulltext/1/001/008/104/892.htmD.F." class="external text" title="http://www.cultinfo.ru/fulltext/1/001/008/104/892.htmD.F." rel="nofollow">Markov and L.I. Timofeev, "Socialist Realism"</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> Sheila Fitzpatrick, <a href="http://books.google.ca/books?id=p2Hxcbxl0OoC&amp;pg=PA209&amp;lpg=PA209&amp;dq=%22girl+meets+tractor%22&amp;source=web&amp;ots=EQyhU0Jbkh&amp;sig=cGMG2SYpULzAY3QGReVzoiTMgrY&amp;hl=en" class="external text" title="http://books.google.ca/books?id=p2Hxcbxl0OoC&amp;pg=PA209&amp;lpg=PA209&amp;dq=%22girl+meets+tractor%22&amp;source=web&amp;ots=EQyhU0Jbkh&amp;sig=cGMG2SYpULzAY3QGReVzoiTMgrY&amp;hl=en" rel="nofollow">The Cultural Front: Power and Culture in Revolutionary Russia</a>, Published 1992 by Cornell University Press, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0801495164" class="internal">ISBN 0801495164</a>.</li>
